import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { Paper, TableContainer, Table, TableHead, TableRow, TableCell, TableBody, Typography, Container, Button } from '@material-ui/core' const Users = ({ users }) => { if (!users) { return null } return( Users User Blogs Created {users.map((user) => ( {user.name} {user.blogs.length} ))}
) } export default Users
